Package com.project.moviebooking.model

package com.project.moviebooking.model
The "model" package houses the domain model classes representing entities and data structures used within the movie booking application.

Model classes in this package encapsulate the core business entities, data structures, and relationships that model the movie booking domain. These classes define the structure and behavior of data elements used within the application, representing real-world concepts and entities.

Organizing model classes in this package helps maintain a clear separation between business entities and the rest of the application, facilitating clean data modeling and improving the overall design and readability of the movie booking system.
